HEADWORD: Tripper
<hw>Trip"per</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
trips or supplants; also, one who walks or trips nimbly; a
dancer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An excursionist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trippet</ent>⟦br⟧
